      <div class="quote-card">
        <h2 id="her-words" class="kicker" style="margin:0 0 6px">From Amari</h2>
        <blockquote>
          <p>It’s an HONOR , to be Recognized by my city. Courageaux Aesthetics came from Joshua 1:9 be courageous for the lord is with you where ever you go. When I left school in New Orleans i understood the demand for skin care in Hammond wasn’t really a thing. Many people thought I couldn’t make money doing this , but I love what I do and my clients recognize it. I was put in position to show people of color we deserve luxury too. Reading text books that didn’t have people that look like me made me want to show the world that corrective skin care IS for us! When I became licensed I promised God that I will handle my Bidness !!</p>
        </blockquote>
        <div class="quote-meta">
          — <strong>Amari Wilford</strong>, Courageaux Aesthetics · <em>Inspiration: Joshua 1:9</em>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="bio">
      <h2 id="bio" class="kicker">Bio</h2>
      <p class="subpara">
        <strong>Amari Wilford</strong> is the licensed esthetician behind Courageaux Aesthetics in Hammond, Louisiana.
        Her approach is calm, disciplined, and results-driven—focused on barrier health, simple routines, and professional
        care you can feel the same day.
      </p>
      <p class="subpara">
        Courageaux serves clients from <strong>Hammond, Ponchatoula, Albany, Independence, and Amite</strong>, with a focus
        on corrective skin care for people of color who deserve luxury, education, and consistency in their skincare journey.
      </p>
      <p class="subpara">
        She also collaborates with Square Bidness on curated wardrobe pieces that match that same “clean, calm, confident”
        energy. Explore the
        <a href="/collections/essentials/" style="font-weight:600">
          Essentials collection
        </a>
        to keep your everyday look aligned with your skin and lifestyle.
      </p>
    </section>
